    {
      "id": "61ec216ab819bcd259254370648cc375198e807e",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 117,
        "name": "Andreas Dilger",
        "email": "adilger@thelustrecollective.com",
        "username": "adilger"
      },
      "date": "2024-08-15 17:45:21.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nPlease don't rename all of the man pages, since the \"nodemap_*\" commands will soon be supplemented by \"nodemap *\" sub-commands via LU-18114.  Instead, please add .so links from \"nodemap_*.8\" to \"nodemap-*.8\" and add these to lustre/doc/Makefile.am so they are included in the RPM/Debian packages.\n\nIt might be worthwhile to test if it is possible to use wildcards in Makefile.am so that \"lctl-lfsck*.8\", \"lctl-nodemap*.8\", etc. can be used to include all matching pages into a package file instead of explicitly listing every man page individually?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "56966916c7fea773905d5f1c26d0c95243d06d81",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 1041,
        "name": "Frederick Dilger",
        "email": "fdilger@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "fdilger"
      },
      "date": "2024-08-16 18:31:16.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n> \n> (1 comment)\n> \n> Please don't rename all of the man pages, since the \"nodemap_*\" commands will soon be supplemented by \"nodemap *\" sub-commands via LU-18114.  Instead, please add .so links from \"nodemap_*.8\" to \"nodemap-*.8\" and add these to lustre/doc/Makefile.am so they are included in the RPM/Debian packages.\n> \n> It might be worthwhile to test if it is possible to use wildcards in Makefile.am so that \"lctl-lfsck*.8\", \"lctl-nodemap*.8\", etc. can be used to include all matching pages into a package file instead of explicitly listing every man page individually?\n\nShould I update the man pages to use a space instead of '_' now or should I wait until LU-18114 is completed/let Emoly update the man pages?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "c53c9e55746d37d60138f2ec58ae0ba69253e012",
      "author": {
